WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.680 --> 00:00:02.240
Nicely done, folks.

2
00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.840
I knew you had it in you.

3
00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:07.000
Looks like the DCI is going to owe you
 a few cakes when she's back in work.

4
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.240
Job's not done, though.

5
00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:11.880
If the DCI can get caught out,
so can anyone.

6
00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:15.040
So make sure you pass on
 all the information and advice

7
00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:16.920
that we've picked up today.

8
00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:20.640
Make sure you, your friends
 and your family are protected online.

9
00:00:21.240 --> 00:00:23.440
Stay safe and well done.

